Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:16.26,mianze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(500,500)}翻譯:虹の夏&熊熊  校對:娜娜莉  特效&後期:JohnTitor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到學園祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去過夏日祭之後 就喜歡上祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你是不是誤會什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭不是那種祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們班的節目是開咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現階段意見分為女僕咖啡店和甜品店兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個喜歡哪一種？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女僕咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}甜品店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不想和你爭執 但是沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算對手是艾莉絲 我也不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不聽我的 晚上就不陪你去洗手間了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在談的和那件事沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:01:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不開甜品店 我就會討厭小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甜食嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女僕嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題有這麼嚴肅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就把兩種混合在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂異文化融合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.76,0:01:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話 我們兩個都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿哈 嘿哈 嘿哈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓身穿女僕裝的小忍坐在神輿上 大家一起來抬神輿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有艾莉絲的祭典風格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種咖啡店…不要哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們班準備演戲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請大家來看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:01:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐也會出演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演什麼角色 是~秘~密~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此 不過你們期待一下還是OK的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你留一個位置的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女優氣場全開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近對於教師來說 笑容也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的老師討學生喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:01.42,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\fad(400,400)\be5\3c&HCEB0D8&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(730.903,456.664)}今天是\N什麼日子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即興搞笑之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…搞笑一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即興搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即興搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圖騰柱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是學園祭的申請書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服裝也由大家一起負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 另外 小路同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 請吐槽我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是在搞笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以吐槽老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到吐槽 有人比我更合適
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豬熊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 怎麼回事怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豬熊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&HBA5F8F&\fs27\fr10\pos(467.725,134)\fad(200,150)}撲\N哧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是金太郎糖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼切 都是金太郎糖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很少見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本的物品都和小忍很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微修改一下長度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們負責製作菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H000000&\fr-25\fs23\pos(517.545,163.066)}咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H000000&\fr-25\fs18\pos(382.925,232.666)}餡料飽滿的花式蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H000000&\fr-25\fs18\pos(339.2,287.333)}巧克力醬糰子串
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H000000&\fr-25\fs18\pos(249.1,328.666)}茶杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H000000&\fr-25\fs18\pos(287.525,382)}綠茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為是我們想出來的菜單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的超市是哪裡來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是北口的超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 小綾 出發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小綾去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去買材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 茶葉就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜豆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糯米粉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天想吃漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 漢堡之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你只是普通朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然這麼說！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 烏丸醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 被你們發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來買學園祭用的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏丸老師呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來買一點零食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間吃會變胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 因為是豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐是零食？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特意連醬油都買了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小路同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想確認一下服裝的號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是穿和服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 因為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豬熊同學和大宮同學說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼想 綾都應該穿這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 別隨隨便便就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然準備工作很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是還真叫人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說來小忍 你還記得明天是什麼日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是學園祭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 說的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 也不是什麼節日呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是誰的生日呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紀念日？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我記得的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於艾莉絲來說是很重要的日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 是什麼日子來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個 艾莉絲第一次開口說話的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次去海邊的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲 艾莉絲在暗示什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想不起來的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲變得無精打采了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 得趕緊想起來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在睡著之前竭盡全力地想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs12\c&H947F6A&\pos(440.783,476.222)}玉米很\N好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs12\c&H8347D5&\pos(166.95,420.666)}奶油增量中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鼓個章魚小嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說人家章魚嘴很失禮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家都生氣著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏賊嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,章魚和烏賊性質上有啥區別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全怪我沒能想起來艾莉絲的什麼紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從昨晚開始她就一直不開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紀念日？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲 我投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 全怪我太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我才該道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 打我一拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會因為衝擊突然就想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 快點 不用手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小忍 已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是小忍來英國家庭寄宿的紀念日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紀念日就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們家每年這個日子都開派對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時的忍真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好多好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且晚餐話題的中心都是關於小忍的回憶故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們家把這天叫做小忍紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年都這樣 哪有那麼多話題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到是我的紀念日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難為情 但是好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 我也想要紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把自己作為女演員出道的這天當作紀念日如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命名為「可憐出道紀念日」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪來的女演員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯卡金像獎得獎紀念日怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,規模不是變得更大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天之內能送出去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維多利亞女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小綾 很適合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歐式茶杯配日本茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日式圓筒茶杯配咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕配紅豆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糰子配巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間咖啡屋就好比我們一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好混沌的咖啡屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲和她的小夥伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有客人來了 快準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 大人們來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進門便是客呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 請挑您喜歡的位子坐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日語好難呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說「主人」可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快快 客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 「主人」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}主主主主主主主…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪門子的效果音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏丸老師 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是滿懷愛意的糰子串
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請品嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師 您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這個 好辣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在其中一串上撒了芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你做了什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 女服務生 真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐看起來很擅長接客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要點些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糰子 還是蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啦客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家可不是商品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我們學校氛圍上差別挺大的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日洋折中？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茶 咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆蛋糕 巧克力糰子各一份是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺可愛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我口味的話 小綾配和服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽子配女僕裝才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 這樣子好可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小綾 小綾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 看我好好說她幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 還是請您不要拍照哇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 勇姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姐姐 你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿和服的艾莉絲 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆換一換豈不更好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是那個意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不啦 小綾還是這樣好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想穿穿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐你們班辦的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看看我的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請務必把我拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又變成了女演員的神態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.31,text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(569.75,176)\fs30\c&H69F1D7&}咖\N啡\N店
