Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到換班的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來參觀一下學園祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 金色的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
